sections.comments: The SIS will enforce automatically prerequisites for this course.  Students will not be able to register themselves if they do not have the correct prerequisites.  If you need to get your UBC file updated with qualifications such as Transfer Credits, take care of that by sending documentation to admissions.inquiry@ubc.ca.

description: Groups, cosets, homomorphisms, group actions, p-groups, Sylow theorems, composition series, finitely generated Abelian groups.
